examples.en: Ideally, this will remove all problems.
The ski slope was situated ideally.
They were ideally suited to one another.
Ideally, your car should have high security locks.
Ideally, the surface should yield slightly under pressure.
He was ideally suited for the job.
Ideally, I'd like to live in New York, but that's not possible.
The hotel is ideally located for enjoying the beauty of Yorkshire.
The city was ideally situated at the crossroads to the great trade centres of Europe.
Fruit and vegetables should ideally be organically grown.
